Human Resources (HR):

Support employee-related cybersecurity policies, onboarding/offboarding processes, and awareness training.

Communications Team Lead:

Facilitate consistent messaging for cybersecurity initiatives and incident response communications.

Vice President of Operations and Corporate Safety:

Ensure operational resilience and safety align with cybersecurity objectives.

Vice President of Engineering and Integrity:

Oversee the integration of cybersecurity into engineering processes and ensure the integrity of systems.

Vice President of Regulatory Affairs:

Ensure compliance with cybersecurity-related regulations and industry standards.

Chief Financial Officer (CFO):

Allocate financial resources for cybersecurity initiatives and assess financial risks associated with cybersecurity threats.

